<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Goodbye from ClarTalk</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background: #121212; /* Dark background as per your app theme */
            color: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ff9800; /* Accent color matching ClarTalk theme */
            margin: 0;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin: 15px 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #e0e0e0;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #121212;
            background: #ff9800; /* Primary button color */
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 147, 64, 0.4);
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: #ad6800;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        .footer {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #ff9800;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Goodbye from ClarTalk</h1>
    <p>
        Thank you for being part of our journey. <br>
        We hope to see you again someday! <br>
        Stay curious, stay bold.
    </p>
    <a href="/" class="btn">Go to Homepage</a>
    <div class="footer">
        &copy; 2025 ClarTalk. Need help? <a href="/contact-us">Contact us</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
